cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.HC, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual representations of brain image data.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also likely as the paper involves analyzing brain connectivity and functional networks.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper discusses interactive visual representations of brain data.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper involves mapping brain surfaces onto 2D and 3D surfaces.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with multiple data sets and modalities.
